    "We addressed this through snowballing by backward and forward searches to identify more relevant articles.",
    "In this way, we also considered articles that were not available in one of the four databases selected at the beginning.",
    "However, articles that used different terminology and was not cited within the set of selected papers may still be missing from our sample even though it may be relevant.",
    "The chance of this occurring is particularly high for newer, less frequently cited papers.",
    "Newer papers using differing terminology were still included though if they cited one of the selected papers due to the forward search in our snowballing approach."
